    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p> And then came the best cabin crew ever. The flight attendant opened his announcement with "Boarding Completed... I think" - we all had to laugh. He was relaxed the whole time, entertaining, warm - just great. We sat at the front, got into conversation, and so the long flight time passed almost in a flash. Particularly nice: from above we could even see the thick clouds above the erupting volcano on La Palma. Impressive - and a bit surreal. </p>
        <p> And so this nice October vacation came to an end. With lots of sun on our faces, sand under our feet, bananas in our stomachs, and a bit of volcanic air in our noses. Tired, but happy. </p>
